      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Usman Bin Isa, from Haroun Bin Kharija, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘(It is) from the reverence that you greet (السَّلَامُ) upon the one you meet’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "12. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ‘Uthman ibn ‘Isa from Harun ibn Kharijah from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “It is of humility to offer the greeting of peace to whomever you meet.” "
        ]
      }
